edu.ata.automation.dispatch

Class UninterruptableAutonomousMode

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ata.automation.dispatch.GameMode
      • edu.ata.automation.dispatch.UninterruptableAutonomousMode
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Autonomous, Runnable

    public abstract class UninterruptableAutonomousMode
extends GameMode
implements Autonomous
    Similar to AutonomousMode, but cannot be 'interrupted'. This is useful in the case of autonomous mode that have the possibility of going over the time limit, but should just continue going until it is done.
    Author:
    Joel Gallant
